name: Play 4
description:
This vignette ends here. 

Upon completing this series I was reminded that this story is my own. I lived a life in and out of the offices but always yearned for one more playful. The fear of that unknown future kept me in line for a long time. After a little hard work and a few strokes of luck, I now live a much more playful life and plan on continuing to do so. If I can, you can.  Play on. Peace out.
